CMSimple_XH
-----------

* fix XH_isAccessProtected() for the single threaded webserver

Building PHP
------------

configure --disable-all --disable-zts --enable-cli --enable-session --enable-json --with-gd --enable-mbstring --with-iconv --with-libxml --with-simplexml --with-xml

php.ini might not be necessary.

PHP
---

* rename php.ini-production to php.ini
* date.timezone = UTC
* extension_dir = "ext"
* enable gd2, intl, mbstring
* zend_extension = php_opcache.dll
* opcache.enable = 1
* sendmail_path = ..\php\php.exe ..\storemail.php
